metadata_z_promoter_why: want to be a ZVENIA Promoter because I am very interested in the mining industry. I enjoy learning and sharing useful information with others. I have experience working in the petrochemical field, and now I study mining engineering. I believe this is a good chance to meet new people, grow my knowledge, and help others in the mining field. I want to support the ZVENIA community and be part of its growth.
metadata_z_promoter_contribute: I can contribute to ZVENIA’s growth by sharing useful posts, videos, and ideas about mining and petrochemical work on platforms like LinkedIn. I will talk about important topics, safety, and new technologies in the mining industry. I can help more people learn about ZVENIA, invite others to join, and build strong connections. With my background in petrochemicals and my current mining engineering studies, I can bring real knowledge and experience to the community.
metadata_z_ads_product_description: We share educational content, technical knowledge, and visual materials related to the mining and petrochemical industries. Our goal is to connect professionals, students, and experts through clear and helpful posts, videos, and blog articles.
